_sText: Gg_boostyard ------------ A fun little map I decided to make; 4 adjacent building each with a enterance and exit teleporter to the opposite building. A ladder on the edge of the buildings to 4 ramps that boost you to the opposing corner. Behind each spawn is a teleporter to the enemies base. Enjoy xD. ------------ 36 Slot. 3D Skybox. Light_env Recommended 2v2+ ------------ Please DL AND ASSESS. Like my work? See more at... tom_tom92's Maplist
